Title: Acceptance
Plot: A death row inmate is felled by an unknown disease and House decides to take on the case, over Cuddy and Foreman's objections. House also has to deal with Stacy who is working closely with him, while Cameron has to cope with a dying patient.
ParentalRatingReason: R13 Violence and content that may disturb
GuestStars: Joseph  Williamson, Mustafa Shakir, Jody Millard, LL Cool J, Michael Dietz, Michael J. Gonzalez, Bryce Johnson, Adrienne Janic, Tony Ross, Christie Lynn Smith, Warren Davis, Anesha  Ndiaye, Marshall Bell
